### ============================================================
### API Parcial 2 - DW | Pruebas HTTP
### Usar con extensión REST Client de VS Code
### Servidor: http://localhost:3000
### ============================================================


### ============================================================
### TABLA: cars (MySQL)
### ============================================================

### [1] GET - Obtener todos los vehículos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cars
Content-Type: application/json

###

### [2] GET BY ID - Obtener vehículo por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cars/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### [3] POST - Crear un nuevo vehículo
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cars
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "marca": "Toyota",
  "clase": "SUV",
  "modelo": 2022,
  "cilindraje": 2.5,
  "capacidad": 5,
  "pago": 85000000
}

###

### [4] PUT - Actualizar vehículo por ID
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/cars/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "marca": "Mazda",
  "clase": "Sedán",
  "modelo": 2023,
  "cilindraje": 2.0,
  "capacidad": 5,
  "pago": 95000000
}

###

### [5] DELETE - Eliminar vehículo por ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/cars/20
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### PRUEBAS DE VALIDACIÓN - cars (deben retornar error 400)
### ============================================================

### [6] POST inválido - marca vacía
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cars
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "marca": "",
  "clase": "SUV",
  "modelo": 2022,
  "cilindraje": 2.5,
  "capacidad": 5,
  "pago": 85000000
}

###

### [7] POST inválido - modelo fuera de rango
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cars
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "marca": "Ford",
  "clase": "Pickup",
  "modelo": 1800,
  "cilindraje": 3.0,
  "capacidad": 4,
  "pago": 50000000
}

###

### [8] POST inválido - pago negativo
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cars
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "marca": "Honda",
  "clase": "Hatchback",
  "modelo": 2020,
  "cilindraje": 1.6,
  "capacidad": 5,
  "pago": -1000
}

###

### [9] POST inválido - campos faltantes
POST http://localhost:3000/api/cars
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "marca": "Kia"
}

###

### [10] GET por ID inexistente - debe retornar 404
GET http://localhost:3000/api/cars/9999
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### TABLA: tuitions (MySQL)
### ============================================================

### [11] GET - Obtener todas las matrículas
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tuitions
Content-Type: application/json

###

### [12] GET BY ID - Obtener matrícula por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tuitions/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### [13] POST - Crear una matrícula
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tuitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date_matricula": "2024-03-15",
  "ciudad": "Bogotá",
  "car_id": 1
}

###

### [14] PUT - Actualizar matrícula
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/tuitions/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date_matricula": "2024-06-20",
  "ciudad": "Medellín",
  "car_id": 2
}

###

### [15] DELETE - Eliminar matrícula
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/tuitions/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### ============================================================
### PRUEBAS DE VALIDACIÓN - tuitions (deben retornar error 400)
### ============================================================

### [16] POST inválido - fecha vacía
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tuitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date_matricula": "",
  "ciudad": "Bogotá",
  "car_id": 1
}

###

### [17] POST inválido - fecha en formato incorrecto
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tuitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date_matricula": "15-03-2024",
  "ciudad": "Cali",
  "car_id": 2
}

###

### [18] POST inválido - ciudad vacía
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tuitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date_matricula": "2024-03-15",
  "ciudad": "",
  "car_id": 1
}

###

### [19] POST inválido - car_id negativo
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tuitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date_matricula": "2024-03-15",
  "ciudad": "Barranquilla",
  "car_id": -5
}

###

### [20] POST inválido - car_id no existe (FK violation)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tuitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date_matricula": "2024-03-15",
  "ciudad": "Santa Marta",
  "car_id": 9999
}

###

### [21] POST inválido - campos faltantes
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tuitions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date_matricula": "2024-03-15"
}

###

### [22] GET por ID inexistente - debe retornar 404
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tuitions/9999
Content-Type: application/json

###
